    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and value. This unit exhibits consistent mechanical integrity and has been preserved with a rigorous attention to detail that ensures immediate road-readiness. Both the exterior finish and interior appointments reflect a high standard of care, making it an exemplary choice for the discerning motorist seeking long-term reliability. This vehicle represents a sophisticated investment for those who demand quality and dependable engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
