      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine. This high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant is paired with a 6-speed G96 manual transaxle, offering precise gear synchronization. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including a ceramic dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced Air-Oil Separator (AOS). The chassis retains its legendary composure thanks to a multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts with refreshed bushings. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers and ventilated, cross-drilled rotors. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the drivetrain is dialed in with no evidence of bore scoring or RMS leaks. A true driver\u2019s car with excellent mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
